    <!-- Check to see if this page is meant to be displaced somewhere else -->
    <line><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0036.01"/>5<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Spirit<anchor
        xml:id="e2-0036.01"/>
      <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">a</del>
        <add place="intralinear">A</add>
      </mod>s over wide dominions</line>
    <line>I sped, like some swift cloud that wings the wide air's wildernesses</line>
    <line>That planet-crested <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">s</del>
        <add place="intralinear">S</add>
      </mod>hape swiftly on lightning-braided pinions</line>
    <line rend="indent1"><mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">Scattered</del>
        <add place="intralinear">Scattering</add>
      </mod> the liquid joy of life from his ambrosial tresses:</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e2-0036.02"/>
    <line>His footsteps paved the world with light <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">?</del>
        <add place="intralinear">&#8212;</add>
      </mod> but as I past 'twas</line>
    <line rend="right">fading</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0036.02"/>
    <line rend="indent1">And hollow Ruin yawned behind &#8212; great Sages bound in madness</line>
    <line>And headless patriots &amp; pale youths who perished unupbraiding</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Gleamed in the <unclear reason="case">N</unclear>ight I wandered o'er
      &#8212; till thou o King of sadness</line>
    <line>Turned by thy smile the worst I said to recollected gladness</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0036.03"/>
    <line rend="center">6.<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Spirit</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0036.03"/>
    <line>Ah sister , Desolation is a delicate thing</line>
    <line>It walks not on the Earth it floats not on the air</line>
    <line>But treads with lulling footstep, &amp; fans with silent wing</line>
    <line>The tender hopes which in thier heart<add>s</add> the best &amp; gentlest bear</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">'Till</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>,</unclear></del>
        <add place="superlinear">Who</add>
      </mod> soothed to false repose by the fanning plumes above</line>
    <line>And the music-stirring motion of its soft &amp; busy feet,</line>
    <line>Dream visions of aerial joy, &amp; call the monster, Love</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e2-0036.04"/>
    <line>And wake, and find their shadow Pain&#8212;as <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">him</del>
        <add place="intralinear">he</add>
      </mod> whom now</line>
    <line rend="right">we greet</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0036.04"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0036.05"/>
    <line rend="center"><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><hi rend="underline">5</hi><hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup"
              >th</hi></hi></del>
        <add place="sublinear">Chorus</add>
      </mod></line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0036.05"/>
    <line rend="indent4"><unclear reason="illegible">X</unclear></line>
    <line rend="indent1">Though Ruin now <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">loves</del>
        <add place="intralinear">Loves</add>
      </mod> shadow be</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Following him, destroyingly</line>
    <line rend="indent2">On Death's white &amp; winged steed</line>
    <line rend="indent2">Which the fleetest cannot flee&#8212;</line>
    <line rend="indent2">Trampling down both flower &amp; weed</line>
    <line rend="left"><add><metamark function="count">769</metamark></add></line>
  </zone>
